                            <comment id="13783810" author="davsclaus" created="Wed, 2 Oct 2013 10:54:11 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;See&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;http://docs.oracle.com/javaee/6/api/javax/jms/Connection.html#close(&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://docs.oracle.com/javaee/6/api/javax/jms/Connection.html#close(&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13783812" author="gtully" created="Wed, 2 Oct 2013 10:56:25 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;issue is concurrent calls to close, some sync is needed.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13783914" author="davsclaus" created="Wed, 2 Oct 2013 13:25:44 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks for reporting. If the connection is closed we no longer throw the illegal state exception.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
